(a)
in january 2011 and prior to the transaction with comcast, we acquired 12.3% of nbcus outstanding shares from vivendi for $3,673 million and made an additional payment of $222 million related to previously purchased shares. of these amounts, $3,070 million reflects a reduction in carrying value of noncontrolling interests. the remaining amount of $825 million represents the amount paid in excess of our carrying value, which was recorded as an increase in our basis in nbcu.
